text: Bling Empire is an American reality television series released on Netflix on January 15, 2021. The series was about the lives of wealthy East and Southeast Asian Americans, socialites in the Los Angeles area. It was compared to the movie Crazy Rich Asians. It is the first American reality television series in which the main cast are all of East and Southeast Asian descent. ==References== Category:2021 American television series debuts Category:Netflix original series Category:American reality television series
